#: ../../source/reference/dataframe/generated/maxframe.dataframe.Series.transform.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.dataframe.Series.transform"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.transform.series_transform:1 of
msgid "Call ``func`` on self producing a Series with transformed values."
msgstr "在自身上调用 ``func`` 以生成一个包含转换值的 Series。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.transform.series_transform:3 of
msgid "Produced Series will have same axis length as self."
msgstr "生成的 Series 将具有与自身相同的轴长度。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.transform.series_transform of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.transform.series_transform:17 of
msgid "Parameter needed for compatibility with DataFrame."
msgstr "为与 DataFrame 兼容而需要的参数。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.transform.series_transform:19 of
msgid "Specify dtypes of returned DataFrames. See `Notes` for more details."
msgstr "指定返回的 DataFrames 的数据类型。详见“说明”部分。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.transform.series_transform:21 of
msgid "Whether infer dtypes when dtypes or output_type is not specified."
msgstr "当未指定 dtypes 或 output_type 时是否推断数据类型。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.transform.series_transform:23 of
msgid "Positional arguments to pass to `func`."
msgstr "传递给 `func` 的位置参数。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.transform.series_transform:24 of
msgid "Keyword arguments to pass to `func`."
msgstr "传递给 `func` 的关键字参数。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.transform.series_transform of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.transform.series_transform:26 of
msgid "* *Series* * *A Series that must have the same length as self.*"
msgstr "* *Series* * *必须与自身具有相同长度的 Series。*"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.transform.series_transform:26 of
msgid "*Series*"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.transform.series_transform:27 of
msgid "*A Series that must have the same length as self.*"
msgstr "*必须与自身具有相同长度的 Series。*"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.transform.series_transform:29 of
msgid ""
":raises ValueError : If the returned Series has a different length than "
"self.:"
msgstr ":raises ValueError : 如果返回的 Series 与自身的长度不同:"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.transform.series_transform:33 of
msgid ":py:obj:`Series.agg`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.transform.series_transform:34 of
msgid "Only perform aggregating type operations."
msgstr "仅执行聚合类型的操作。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.transform.series_transform:36 of
msgid ":py:obj:`Series.apply`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.transform.series_transform:37 of
msgid "Invoke function on a Series."
msgstr "在 Series 上调用函数。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.transform.series_transform:40 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.misc.transform.series_transform:41 of
msgid ""
"When deciding output dtypes and shape of the return value, MaxFrame will "
"try applying ``func`` onto a mock Series, and the transform call may "
"fail. When this happens, you need to specify ``dtype`` of output Series."
msgstr ""
"在确定输出数据类型和返回值形状时，MaxFrame 会尝试将 ``func`` 应用于一个"
"模拟 Series，此时 transform 调用可能会失败。发生这种情况时，您需要指定"
"输出 Series 的 ``dtype``。"

